      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_23_4724-4806",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "4724-4806",
      "markText": "他带来的一只行李箱中塞满了准备留下来穿的换洗衣物，另一只一样的箱子里装着她写给他的近两千封信。信件按照日期码放得齐齐整整，每一捆都用彩色绸带系好，一封也没有拆开过。",
      "totalCount": 9418,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=4724&rangeEnd=4806",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=4724&rangeEnd=4806"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_15_4319-4412",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "4319-4412",
      "markText": "“他的身体比我们都健康，但给他听诊时，可以听见眼泪在他心里翻腾。”他不仅将房子连同里面的一切都卖给了巴亚尔多·圣罗曼，而且请求他一点一点地付钱，因为他甚至没有一个能存放这么多钞票的箱子。",
      "totalCount": 5328,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4319&rangeEnd=4412",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=4319&rangeEnd=4412"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_15_2145-2225",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "2145-2225",
      "markText": "最重要的角色无疑是他的父亲佩特罗尼奥·圣罗曼将军，他是上个世纪内战中的英雄，因为在图库林卡事件中击败奥雷里亚诺·布恩迪亚上校，而成为保守党政权最显赫的人物之一。",
      "totalCount": 5109,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2145&rangeEnd=2225",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=2145&rangeEnd=2225"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_27_4718-4735",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "4718-4735",
      "markText": "“他们把我杀了，韦内姑娘。”他说。",
      "totalCount": 4624,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=4718&rangeEnd=4735",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=4718&rangeEnd=4735"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_17_947-1007",
      "chapterUid": 17,
      "range": "947-1007",
      "markText": "不过根据种种事实推断，兄弟两人似乎并不想避开众人立刻杀死圣地亚哥·纳萨尔，而是千方百计让人出面阻止他们，只不过没有成功。",
      "totalCount": 4420,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=17&rangeStart=947&rangeEnd=1007",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=17&rangeStart=947&rangeEnd=1007"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_15_9458-9534",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "9458-9534",
      "markText": "她在黑暗中搜寻，只一眼便从这个世界与另一个世界众多极易混淆的姓名中找到了它。她用精准的飞镖将它钉在墙上，仿佛它是一只没有意志的蝴蝶，对它的审判早已写就。",
      "totalCount": 3978,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=9458&rangeEnd=9534",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=9458&rangeEnd=9534"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_14_8004-8032",
      "chapterUid": 14,
      "range": "8004-8032",
      "markText": "她实在难以料到，仅仅为了取悦她，他竟然买下了所有的彩票。",
      "totalCount": 3438,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=14&rangeStart=8004&rangeEnd=8032",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=14&rangeStart=8004&rangeEnd=8032"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_27_4814-4847",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "4814-4847",
      "markText": "他从那扇自六点钟起就敞开的后门进了家，随后脸朝下倒在了厨房的地上。",
      "totalCount": 3068,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=4814&rangeEnd=4847",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=27&rangeStart=4814&rangeEnd=4847"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_13_386-467",
      "chapterUid": 13,
      "range": "386-467",
      "markText": "圣地亚哥·纳萨尔被杀的那一天，清晨五点半就起了床，去迎候主教乘坐的船。夜里他梦见自己穿过一片飘着细雨的榕树林，梦中他感到片刻的快慰，将醒来时却觉得浑身都淋了鸟粪。",
      "totalCount": 3047,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=13&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=467",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=13&rangeStart=386&rangeEnd=467"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_22_433-492",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "433-492",
      "markText": "更糟糕的是，神父将破碎的肠子全部掏了出来，后来竟然不知该如何处理，只好对着它们气恼地祷告了一番，然后全部扔进了垃圾桶。",
      "totalCount": 2992,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=433&rangeEnd=492",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=433&rangeEnd=492"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_15_7551-7607",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "7551-7607",
      "markText": "很多人都记得，我趁着醉酒欢闹向梅塞德斯·巴尔恰求婚，那时候她刚刚读完小学，正像十四年后我们结婚时她提醒我的那样。",
      "totalCount": 2916,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=7551&rangeEnd=7607",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=7551&rangeEnd=7607"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_19_2971-3034",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "2971-3034",
      "markText": "许多人装作顾客来买他们根本不需要的牛奶，询问店里没有的吃食，实际上是想看看，兄弟俩是否真的在等圣地亚哥·纳萨尔，准备要杀了他。",
      "totalCount": 2834,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2971&rangeEnd=3034",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=2971&rangeEnd=3034"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300020482_19_1195-1237",
      "chapterUid": 19,
      "range": "1195-1237",
      "markText": "对于佩德罗像得了勋章一样到处炫耀大人物才患的淋病，巴勃罗·维卡里奥甚至觉得很是光彩。",
      "totalCount": 2756,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300020482&chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1195&rangeEnd=1237",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4432e10813ab6e80g01239a?chapterUid=19&rangeStart=1195&rangeEnd=1237"
